&nbsp;<br />
Have you ever felt like quitting? What made you continue? <a href="http://ctt.ec/6eth8" target="_blank">Click to Tweet.</a><br />
&nbsp;<br />
Suffering setbacks? Taking forever to make progress? You&#8217;re not alone. <a href="http://ctt.ec/aXmGW" target="_blank">Click to Tweet.</a><br />
